# Repo-root Docker build context (used only by the inference-api image, whose
# context is the repo root so it can COPY helpers/model_loading.py). Everything
# heavy or irrelevant to that image is excluded so the daemon receives only
# source — without this the context would be ~6.7GB (.venv + data + ...).
#
# NOTE: only builds whose context is the repo root are affected by this file.
# The airflow/mlflow/ray images build from their own infra/ subdir contexts and
# are unaffected.

# Virtualenvs / interpreters
.venv/
.venv-test/
test-01/

# Large data + model artifacts (the inference image pulls models from MLflow, not disk)
data/
mlruns/
orig_dataset/
*.joblib
*.npz
*.parquet
*.csv

# Generated / tooling
ui-eval/
node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.git/
.claude/
.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Docs / notebooks not needed at serve time
*.ipynb
docs/
*.html
